gw.api.claim

Class OwnedRelatedClaimFilterSetBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.filters.FilterSetBase
      • gw.api.claim.ClaimFilterSetBase
        • gw.api.claim.OwnedRelatedClaimFilterSetBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DesktopClaimFilterSet, TeamClaimFilterSet, VacationClaimFilterSet

    public abstract class OwnedRelatedClaimFilterSetBase
extends ClaimFilterSetBase
    Abstract claim filter set that adds compound filters based on owned and related claims to the ClaimFilterSetBase. The owned and related filter sets are abstract and must be provided by subclassers
